The paper proposes a new model for time series prediction that utilizes convolutional layers for feature extraction, a recurrent encoder, and a linear autoregressive component. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the use of convolutional layers suggests that the paper may also belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with time series data, which suggests that it may also belong to the statistics (cs.ST) sub-category.
